snippet.textDisplay:
Hi, April. I'm not sure if I've ever commented over the years of watching you but now, I can't hold back my excitement.
I am SO happy for you! To see your excitement and enthusiasm is truly exhilarating. From vanities, to fold down work benches,
to fences to chicken coops, not to mention that AWESOME shop! It has been irreplaceable time in front of this monitor.
Watching your thoughts and dreams come to fruition has been amazing. Your parents must be busting at the seams at how
proud they are of you. Heck, I don't even know you and I'M proud of you!
May you always be happy. May you always be healthy and may you always, always be blessed.
Keep smiling and have a happy heart. Thank you for sharing this awesome ride with us!
